/香港足球因為正面原因<br />\n喺本地媒體曝光多兩次<br />\n電視都有報導<br />\n對外<br />\n鄭展龍本人可以喺AFC網站有個簡短訪問<br />\n而AFC社交媒體喺疫情期間都有翻炒<br />\n<br />\n一切只係緣於大家認真對待呢d投票<br />\n一味話香港足球無得救<br />\n係於事無補<br />\n我相信每人既細微舉動<br />\n都可以為香港足球帶黎影響<br />\nFrom: 數字球"},{"pid":"8c8ada65e5b83859cd4913f1a413da2af35bc142","tid":2247992,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"暫時嘅投票走勢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fE7NweD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfE7NweD.png&h=b7a7219e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bba3150c5cb858c7bca59c1a49ad82c58bd97451","tid":2247992,"uid":20279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"54095f460d8365169447d151c68f2292d065f9e9","tid":2247992,"uid":20279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"上熱門"},{"pid":"b0360b01e13477d1e3b4599488be6bbacd694e78","tid":2247992,"uid":20279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"回覆速度太快請稍後嘗試"},{"pid":"5dbbec3ca295d0ee401acf9369c076d5351b4b8e","tid":2247992,"uid":20279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:48:47.000Z","msg":"但係呢球AV真係勁好多"},{"pid":"296d7ea8b01bd22dae5e1d8a9687af18aee53fa4","tid":2247992,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0360b01e13477d1e3b4599488be6bbacd694e78","tid":2247992,"uid":20279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"回覆速度太快請稍後嘗試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f27535d5a6b22bea0fa6532fa31085e181f01df","tid":2247992,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"嘉緯喺新一季港超聯加盟咗標準流浪<br />\n最近踢嘅一場比賽係尋晚嘅2020東南海盃公開組8強<br />\n標準對和團，最後賽果係標準 2-0 和團<br />\n白衫10號就係嘉緯<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z_onVRPlSos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz_onVRPlSos&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=f2c72149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z_onVRPlSos</a>"},{"pid":"26dbdecbbac6035daddbafe9e5f09e92aa866e2d","tid":2247992,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:30:54.000Z","msg":"石硤尾街場出身，踢到穿上香港隊10號球衣的「林嘉緯」，無論在石地足球界甚至在香港近代足球歷史，已經是傳奇的存在。「林嘉緯」這三個字，象徵「技術和傳控足球」。說得更精準一點，是在著重體力的香港職業足球環境下，仍然能憑「技術和傳控足球」成為獨當一面的球員的象徵。憑他於職業和國際賽的表現，成為石硤尾最重要和最具代表性的球員。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SouthEastSeaCup/posts/1495274494000551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSouthEastSeaCup%2Fposts%2F1495274494000551&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=ba9a1488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SouthEastSeaCup/posts/1495274494000551</a><br />\nFrom: 本地足球"},{"pid":"dd8ddd3164fea0488ac61e42adf5f27b9067f370","tid":2247992,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T11:10:24.000Z","msg":"CLS 嘉緯喺2017年做嘅訪問<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-IwtBBVpHQI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-IwtBBVpHQI&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=2400184b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-IwtBBVpHQI</a>"},{"pid":"3cdbf423baa6f9a07731a7e0a639b9c0faa62463","tid":2247992,"uid":23763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dbbec3ca295d0ee401acf9369c076d5351b4b8e","tid":2247992,"uid":20279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:48:47.000Z","msg":"但係呢球AV真係勁好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"另外嗰球太碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101227034a4552ee2a07ff0bbb3840b775a36094","tid":2247992,"uid":297439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T11:30:44.000Z","